# **Privacy Policy**

## **1. Information We Collect**
BarrelBook stores your whiskey collection data, tasting notes, and app preferences locally on your device.

## **2. How We Use Your Information**
Your data is used solely to provide the BarrelBook service functionality and analytics about your whiskey collection.

## **3. Data Security**
Your data is encrypted and stored securely on your device. We do not have access to your personal whiskey collection data.

## **4. Third Party Services**
BarrelBook uses Apple's App Store for subscription management and payment processing. These services are governed by Apple's privacy policy and terms of service.

## **5. Data Deletion**
You can delete your data at any time by deleting the app from your device.

## **6. Contact Us**
If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through the app's support section.

